rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0002
rows.name: How did we end up with a food shortage?

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0003
rows.name:
You're the lord of this
whole region, aren't you?

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Aletta is in the Iiran frontier.
It's got a much smaller
population than the capital.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0006
rows.name:
We had some supplies stored up, but
with the whole resistance army
descending on us, they ran out fast.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0007
rows.name:
I can't force the people of
Aletta to provide for us. It's
up to us to handle this, right?

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0008
rows.name: I guess that makes some sense...

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0009
rows.name:
We're going to be staying here for
a bit, so we should help solve it.

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Adel-sama, give me and Sata
something to do, too!

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0012
rows.name: We'll at least earn our own keep!

rows.label: campfev11_400_150_msg0013
rows.name:
Haha... thanks, everyone.
You're all so dependable.
